metadata.name: The Other Side /2
metadata.description:
The other side 

Behind what you see  
Behind this frame 
,  
There is a girl 
Or maybe a boy  
There is a moment...  
You may never know who's 
You may never know what goes 
,  
What you see  
Is a shadow of what u have never lived!

HamideH  
18/January/2023
